# Unreal Engine Standard Gitignore

# --- Unreal Engine Temporary / Generated Files ---
# Project root or subfolder temp files
Binaries/
Build/
DerivedDataCache/
Intermediate/
Saved/
FileOpenOrder/
.vs/
*.sln
*.suo
*.opensdf
*.sdf
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb
*.ignore
*.pyc

# Nested folder temp files (Matches any subfolder)
**/Binaries/
**/Build/
**/DerivedDataCache/
**/Intermediate/
**/Saved/

# --- OS Specific Files ---
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.out
Thumb.db

# --- Build Artifacts ---
*.apk
*.ipa
*.pdb
*.obj
*.exe

# --- Large Files & Assets ---
# Note: GitHub has a 100MB limit per file. 
# It is highly recommended to use Git LFS for the following extensions:
# *.uasset
# *.umap
# *.zip
# *.psd

# If you are manually splitting large files into parts (e.g., .001, .002), 
# you can track them while ignoring the original large source file.
# Example: 
# /BigFile.zip (Add this to ignore)
# /BigFile.zip.00* (This will be tracked)
